race.description: Williams Crane Hire (N/P) Tg 5+W Series F Pr2 Divi
race.comment: RITZA WOTTON (5) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (35.41) in a Special conditions race over 595m at Angle Park. Has the ability and looks hard to top. SILK SONIC (2) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when second (29.94) at this track in a Other. Can turn it around this time. KIA KEEPING (8) is yet to miss the placings here in an excellent record which boasts two wins. Placed last time (23.53) at this track in a TG1-4W, finishing second and beaten 5.5 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. LOCHINVAR PEARL (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
